J.A., Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
DEPT. OF CHILDREN & FAMILIES, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D17-3983 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. February 08, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Because J.A. has failed to serve an initial brief as provided by this court's order of December 28, 2017, this appeal is dismissed for failure to prosecute.

VILLANTI, BADALAMENTI, and ROTHSTEIN-YOUAKIM, JJ., Concur.
